{"tid":347779,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"得罪講句，爭鮮真係垃圾","createTime":"2017-08-05T06:11:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-05T19:58:44.000Z","uid":45637,"like":8,"dislike":60,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"637cb95430c7b0bc1797dfe5920c69a96ba0246e","tid":347779,"uid":45637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T06:11:20.000Z","msg":"是咁的，今日買左盒爭鮮當lunch<br />\n我食左四舊，決定唔再食落去<br />\n我忍受唔到，將一啲唔新鮮既材料，再加埋舊冷飯放入口既感覺<br />\n仲要諷刺地，個名叫做爭鮮<br />\n又諗起以前細個，呀媽會自己卷壽司，材料無咩特別，只係蟹柳同腸仔<br />\n但加上媽媽既用心，配上一舊溫暖既飯，就已經好足夠<br />\n依家岀左黎做野好多年，媽媽都離開左我了<br />\n望住眼前冰冷既爭鮮，同回憶既溫暖形成強烈對比<br />\n然後我又再食一舊爭鮮，吃下一啖回憶"},{"pid":"0b8c85e3db7cc72e64b1760552b1771089da3b0d","tid":347779,"uid":126436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T06:12:47.000Z","msg":"重作"},{"pid":"6c1a37b8e4b3adf3ba234a6be0814e964159ef81","tid":347779,"uid":4213,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T06:13:39.000Z","msg":"1分啦 太煽情變到啲叫春文咁"},{"pid":"c1ab54d32e0b971a4f51742f6a4a362e155c2467","tid":347779,"uid":29523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T06:16:34.000Z","msg":"無&ldquo;是咁的&rdquo;開頭，零分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2250875869006ef29a0ef9fbe08892acb6a539e","tid":347779,"uid":46435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T06:17:04.000Z","msg":"啲壽司飯凍既 0分"},{"pid":"8d34cdc1140b64b5e234e4d3b31b180eb9124652","tid":347779,"uid":77904,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T06:17:37.000Z","msg":"個轉合咁差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f158a8b0afb798db0f7baeef426c2e84d889d92b","tid":347779,"uid":29523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T06:18:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>無&ldquo;是咁的&rdquo;開頭，零分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n未打完出左post <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n講緊最後個段叫春文